IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. SAMPLEBILL.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  CUSTOMER-NAME      PIC A(20).
       01  AMOUNT-DUE         PIC 9(5)V99.
       01  PAYMENT-RECEIVED   PIC 9(5)V99.
       01  BALANCE            PIC S9(5)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-INITIALIZE.
           DISPLAY "STARTING BILLING PROGRAM".
           MOVE "JOHN DOE" TO CUSTOMER-NAME.
           MOVE 100.00 TO AMOUNT-DUE.
           MOVE 0 TO PAYMENT-RECEIVED.
           MOVE AMOUNT-DUE TO BALANCE.
           PERFORM 1000-ACCEPT-PAYMENT.

       1000-ACCEPT-PAYMENT.
           DISPLAY "ENTER PAYMENT RECEIVED: ".
           ACCEPT PAYMENT-RECEIVED.
           SUBTRACT PAYMENT-RECEIVED FROM BALANCE.
           PERFORM 2000-DISPLAY-BALANCE.

       2000-DISPLAY-BALANCE.
           DISPLAY "CUSTOMER: " CUSTOMER-NAME.
           DISPLAY "BALANCE DUE: " BALANCE.
           IF BALANCE <= 0
               DISPLAY "ACCOUNT PAID IN FULL"
           ELSE
               DISPLAY "PAYMENT STILL DUE".
           STOP RUN.